title: Free tickets to Fort Lauderdale Strikers vs. San Antonio Scorpions on Wednesday, Oct. 21
text:
Get up to four free tickets to the Fort Lauderdale Strikers game on Wednesday, Oct. 21, compliments of WSFL-Ch. 39.
Get the free general admission tickets to see the Strikers take on the San Antonio Scorpions at 7:30 p.m. at Lockhart Stadium in Fort Lauderdale.
Wednesday is Zombie Night at the stadium, so wear your goriest costume to get on TV. WSFL broadcasts Striker games live.
Click here for the deal. Pick up tickets at the Will Call window.
